  "description": "The Ration Lockroom is a narrow storage chamber cut into the Riftwarden Apartment’s ferrocrete superstructure, its void-black reinforcement ribs exposed between sealed conduit runs. Wall-mounted shelving and strap-down rails line the length of the room, arranged for standardized crates and issued canisters under quarantine handling rules. An inner bulkhead hatch carries gasketed seams and a placard rail for inventory seals, while armored lumen diffusers maintain a cold, constant illumination over scuffed deck plating.",
